Finally… @nockingpoint & @rootsoffight have come together with a spectacular Pinot Grigio from our friend and trusted winemaker Sean Boyd.

Check out nockingpoint.com and get your hands on some right away!!

My Uncle Paul and his buddies have created an eco-certified, reusable cotton bamboo mask. A portion of their proceeds are going to support @envirodefence, a Canadian charitable organization that is working towards reducing plastic pollution. Check them out @eco6ix! 

www.eco6ix.ca

node.text:
We make a big deal out of big deals and selling out of a wine is a big deal. Pink Wine For Dudes is gone... but it’s coming back in May. In the meantime, I’ve got a message for all the folks who love wine / support @NockingPoint.

#NockingPoint #SoldOut #PinkWine
